  "text": "To facilitate a comparison between the model and data, we focus our analysis on the effect of host body size and temperature, taking advantage of the fact that many key parameters of the model are likely to be allometric functions of host body size and temperature. In particular, host carrying capacities (K j ), maximum per-capita reproductive rates (r j ) and mortality rates (m j ) will scale with host body size and temperature [CITATION_1] as",
